High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. It has been custom painted with a knotwork dragon. 200 keys could never unlock its secrets.
The M4A4 | 龍王 (Dragon King) was first introduced to CS:GO 8 years ago, on January 8th, 2015. It was released as part of the Chroma Case, alongside the Full Spectrum update.

Luxe Operator was first added to the game in Episode 01: Ignition. This skin is Select upgradable Operator skin. It should be noted that there's an option to get this skin via the in-game store. This skin is from Luxe collection.

The AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is reliable and has a lot of power. It is most dangerous when it fires in short, controlled bursts. The Empress tarot card was used as inspiration for the painting.

Non-upgradable skin from the Ignition : Act 1 Battlepass Chapter 1 Tier 5. The skin have a unique texture, and it is entirely cosmetic, without affecting the gameplay. The skin is available since June 2, 2020.
